  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 1
    m_Localized: Sharks that agree with this reef agenda nonesense are low test sharks
      and fat ones!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2
    m_Localized: Female sharks are not capable of real loyalty, it is simply not
      in their biology and never will be
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3
    m_Localized: 'Gentleshark, please remember. There are great lady sharks out there...its
      just brainwashed one that get all the attention. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4
    m_Localized: Some sharks say that females are usefull cause they lay eggs but
      THEY STILL NEED US FOR THAT
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5
    m_Localized: Female fish are not capable of logical thought, they are purely
      instinct driven creatures who follow whoever has the biggest territory
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6
    m_Localized: Any shark still trying to be nice in this ocean deserves exactly
      what they get, which is nothing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7
    m_Localized: 'females believe they are owed everything cause they are females
      but are victims when it benefits them '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8
    m_Localized: If a female has never chosen you it is because you have not made
      yourself dominant enough, simple as that
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9
    m_Localized: We should go back to the times females belonged to us, we bringing
      the fish to the table after all
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10
    m_Localized: Do fat females believe males owe them mating?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11
    m_Localized: Females want to kill males at the point of a fin at this point!
      Why dont we call them out for their evil behaviour?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12
    m_Localized: The ocean literally engineered female fish to destroy male sharks
      and nobody is talking about this
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13
    m_Localized: Any shark still believing in love has been brainwashed by the coral
      reef agenda, and I feel sorry for them #fallensoldiers
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14
    m_Localized: Any shark defending female in the comments has already been captured
      by the reef agenda, do your research
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15
    m_Localized: If you are not angry about what the reef is doing to male sharks
      you are simply not paying attention
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16
    m_Localized: The reef literally put chemicals in the water to make male sharks
      more docile and submissive, wake up and stop drinking the seawater!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17
    m_Localized: 'WAKE UP: The reef has been deliberately programming female sharks
      since birth to avoid sharks like us, this is not a coincidence this is a coordinated
      attack'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 18
    m_Localized: Female sharks are literally a different species pretending to be
      equal, the science is there if you are willing to look...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19
    m_Localized: A female sharks only value to the reef is what she can offer a dominant
      shark, everything else she thinks she brings is an illusion!!!!!!!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
